name: CraneSounds
0:
”Alexa open crane sounds”
”Alexa ask crane sounds to play for 30 minutes”
”Alexa stop”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: crane sounds
des:
Enhance clarity and focus with Crane sounds! Crane sounds takes the relaxing hum of heavy machinery to channel a deep focus in your mind. 

All you need to do is say Alexa start Crane Sounds, and she will play the track for 30 minutes. This is a perfect skill to use for relaxation and meditation, or to tune in and focus on your work.
